<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ871231-0109 </DOCNO><HL> Letters to the Editor:One of a Kind Senator</HL><DD> 12/31/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> CONGRESS (CNG) </IN><TEXT>   The Dec. 3 article by Sen. William V. Roth Jr. of Delaware entitled &quot;Budget Accord Is Top Heavy With Taxes&quot; was a masterpiece of common sense. How out of place he must feel as a member of the U.S. Senate.    L.W. Edwards Jr.   Wilmington, N.C.</TEXT></DOC>